author: Jill Layton
title: Hilary Duff has joined the intense brow game, is winning already
text:
Hilary Duff has joined the intense brow game, is winning already Thick, bold eyebrows are all the rage right now. Gone are the days of thin, demure brows from the ’90s — at least according to faces like Cara Delevingne, Keira Knightley, Lily Collins, Emilia Clarke and the newest addition to the bold brow club: Hilary Duff .
Duff debuted her new, bolder brows on Snapchat . It’s unclear if the brows are sticking around for good, or if she was like, in the middle of getting them dyed.
But either way, it’s a new look for her that we’re kind of digging. She Snapped her dark brows, writing “Bitch brow in progress,” and she’s not wrong. The brows definitely make her look a little harder and ready to throw down if she needs to. But like, in the least aggressive way possible, because come on, she’s still Hilary Duff.
Hilary Duff/ Snapchat In case you forget what her regular brows look like, here’s a reminder:
A photo posted by Hilary Duff (@hilaryduff) on Dec 1, 2016 at 9:18am PST 

And here’s another shot of Duff’s brows that are pretty much perfection as is:
A photo posted by Hilary Duff (@hilaryduff) on Jan 13, 2017 at 10:37am PST 
But it never hurts to mix things up again, and “bitch brows” are certainly one way of doing that.
More brows:
A photo posted by Hilary Duff (@hilaryduff) on Dec 26, 2016 at 8:47am PST 
TBH, her brows are always immaculate looking. Even if she does get them professionally done, for being a mom of two kids with a busy career, perfect brows are always impressive.
